			<div class="bar_green PL10" id="print_parts">
				<p class="news_content_date">2018-10-13</p>
				<h2>【明鏡洞】年度掌中戲鉅獻：明鏡洞五俠傳奇</h2>
				<h4></h4>
                <div id="media_contents" class="w80 container">
	                	                <p class="text-center font_green">
		                <i>
		                	〞「五俠傳奇助選團」是民進黨這次選戰唯一一個全由虛擬角色組成的助選團。〞
						</i>
					</p>
										<hr>
	                <p>
	<span style="font-size:16px;"><img alt="" src="/upload/ckfinder/images/WhatsApp%20Image%202018-10-11%20at%203_51_46%20PM(1).jpeg" style="width: 848px; height: 1200px;" /></span></p>
<p>
	<span style="font-size:16px;">【年度掌中戲鉅獻：明鏡洞五俠傳奇】</span></p>
<p>
	<span style="font-size:16px;">全力應戰九合一選舉，民進黨將陸續推出六個「助選團」在全國各地亮相，向民眾介紹本黨候選人的理念與施政佳績。</span></p>
<p>
	<span style="font-size:16px;">「五俠傳奇助選團」是這次選戰唯一一個全由虛擬角色組成的助選團。讓政策議題轉化為布袋戲英雄人物，道出一段關於堅持與抉擇的傳奇故事。</span></p>
<div class="text_exposed_show">
	<p>
		<span style="font-size:16px;">《明鏡洞五俠傳奇》的世界裡，結合了科幻、奇幻、推理與穿越劇等元素，什麼都有、什麼都不奇怪！敬請期待，「明鏡洞電視台」年度掌中戲鉅獻！</span></p>
	<p>
		<span style="font-size:16px;">【劇情搶先看】<br />
		秘密組織「車輪會」欲圖謀再起，重掌仙島！車輪會欲在一不為人知之處，開啟異次元結界，引入異星勢力，讓仙島萬劫不復。</span></p>
	<p>
		<span style="font-size:16px;">仙島有一山洞，洞內礦物閃閃發光，人稱為「明鏡洞」。洞裡居住五名武藝高強的曠世英雄，練就五大改革絕技。</span></p>
	<p>
		<span style="font-size:16px;">明鏡洞五俠，是否能阻止車輪會死灰復燃？緊張緊張緊張、刺激刺激刺激！且看五俠如何使出絕技：<a class="_58cn" data-ft="{" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/%E6%8C%BA%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9?source=feed_text&amp;__xts__%5B0%5D=68.ARAv8YtE60l673HZCVUeR_1QDpSPh5-ruWnkX3Oq0fKq46Ortz7A4F0wUW7rIhQ7sjZj08MqdA45L6FYIGBCHhO3cTYGbARg0_P6APAhXYVRuJ2c11Zu8XEDEmvmlewIX5dxmM5J2dRfrVEfBKs63iGoi9d07ZAEP_1t-ROyGn_gISzo-BDGiFo&amp;__tn__=%2ANK-R"><span class="_5afx"><span aria-label="主題標籤" class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">挺改革</span></span></a> <a class="_58cn" data-ft="{" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/%E6%8B%9A%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F?source=feed_text&amp;__xts__%5B0%5D=68.ARAv8YtE60l673HZCVUeR_1QDpSPh5-ruWnkX3Oq0fKq46Ortz7A4F0wUW7rIhQ7sjZj08MqdA45L6FYIGBCHhO3cTYGbARg0_P6APAhXYVRuJ2c11Zu8XEDEmvmlewIX5dxmM5J2dRfrVEfBKs63iGoi9d07ZAEP_1t-ROyGn_gISzo-BDGiFo&amp;__tn__=%2ANK-R"><span class="_5afx"><span aria-label="主題標籤" class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">拚經濟</span></span></a> <a class="_58cn" data-ft="{" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/%E6%96%B0%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90?source=feed_text&amp;__xts__%5B0%5D=68.ARAv8YtE60l673HZCVUeR_1QDpSPh5-ruWnkX3Oq0fKq46Ortz7A4F0wUW7rIhQ7sjZj08MqdA45L6FYIGBCHhO3cTYGbARg0_P6APAhXYVRuJ2c11Zu8XEDEmvmlewIX5dxmM5J2dRfrVEfBKs63iGoi9d07ZAEP_1t-ROyGn_gISzo-BDGiFo&amp;__tn__=%2ANK-R"><span class="_5afx"><span aria-label="主題標籤" class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">新能源</span></span></a> <a class="_58cn" data-ft="{" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/%E5%A5%BD%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83?source=feed_text&amp;__xts__%5B0%5D=68.ARAv8YtE60l673HZCVUeR_1QDpSPh5-ruWnkX3Oq0fKq46Ortz7A4F0wUW7rIhQ7sjZj08MqdA45L6FYIGBCHhO3cTYGbARg0_P6APAhXYVRuJ2c11Zu8XEDEmvmlewIX5dxmM5J2dRfrVEfBKs63iGoi9d07ZAEP_1t-ROyGn_gISzo-BDGiFo&amp;__tn__=%2ANK-R"><span class="_5afx"><span aria-label="主題標籤" class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">好社會</span></span></a> <a class="_58cn" data-ft="{" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/%E5%8A%A9%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4?source=feed_text